      <title>云计算搭建初始环境（Centos7）</title>
      <link href="/2023/08/05/%E4%BA%91%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%88%9D%E5%A7%8B%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%EF%BC%88Centos7%EF%BC%89/"/>
      <url>/2023/08/05/%E4%BA%91%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%88%9D%E5%A7%8B%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%EF%BC%88Centos7%EF%BC%89/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="搭建初始环境（CentOS7初始环境）"><a href="#搭建初始环境（CentOS7初始环境）" class="headerlink" title="搭建初始环境（CentOS7初始环境）"></a>搭建初始环境（CentOS7初始环境）</h1><h3 id="一、-修改主机名"><a href="#一、-修改主机名" class="headerlink" title="一、 修改主机名"></a>一、 修改主机名</h3><h5 id="Compute"><a href="#Compute" class="headerlink" title="Compute"></a>Compute</h5><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Hostnamectl set-hostname compute</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h5 id="Controller"><a href="#Controller" class="headerlink" title="Controller"></a>Controller</h5><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Hostnamectl set-hostname controller</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="二、-配置vsftp服务"><a href="#二、-配置vsftp服务" class="headerlink" title="二、 配置vsftp服务"></a>二、 配置vsftp服务</h3><h5 id="将ios镜像文件传输到linux云主机上"><a href="#将ios镜像文件传输到linux云主机上" class="headerlink" title="将ios镜像文件传输到linux云主机上"></a>将ios镜像文件传输到linux云主机上</h5><p>连接至云主机，在本机使用put将文件传输</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">C:\Users\17458&gt; sftp root@192.168.40.128</span><br><span class="line">root@192.168.40.128&#x27;s password:</span><br><span class="line">Connected to 192.168.40.128.</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta prompt_">sftp&gt; </span><span class="language-bash">put C:\Users\17458\Desktop\CentOS-7-x86_64-DVD-2009.iso(文件在本机路径)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta prompt_">sftp&gt; </span><span class="language-bash">put C:\Users\17458\Desktop\cloud_iaas.iso(文件在本机路径)</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>在云主机创建两个文件夹 centos iaas</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">mkdir /opt/centos</span><br><span class="line">mkdir /opt/iaas</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>挂载iso镜像**(挂载和去除挂载时不能再挂载点目录下执行)**</p><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">mount /root/CentOS-7-x86_64-DVD-2009.iso /mnt</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> /mnt/Packages/</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#安装vsftp服务</span></span><br><span class="line">rpm -ivh vsftpd-3.0.2-28.el7.x86_64.rpm</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#将挂载后内部文件转移到centos文件夹下</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cp</span> -rvf /mnt/* /opt/centos</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#去除挂载</span></span><br><span class="line">umount -v /mnt</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#挂载iaas镜像</span></span><br><span class="line">mount /root/cloud_iaas.iso /opt/iaas</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#将挂载后内部文件转移到iaas文件夹下</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cp</span> -rvf /mnt/* /opt/centos</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#去除挂载</span></span><br><span class="line">umount -v /mnt</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>修改vsftpd.conf</p><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">vi /etc/vsftpd/vsftpd.conf</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#文件末尾添加如下配置(不能有空格)</span></span><br><span class="line">anon_root=/opt</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#启动vsftpd服务</span></span><br><span class="line"> systemctl start vsftpd</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#开机自启vsftpd服务</span></span><br><span class="line">systemctl <span class="built_in">enable</span> vsftpd</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#查看vsftpd服务状态</span></span><br><span class="line">systemctl status vsftpd</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="三、-Yum源配置"><a href="#三、-Yum源配置" class="headerlink" title="三、 Yum源配置"></a>三、 Yum源配置</h3><p>配置hosts映射文件</p><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">vi /etc/hosts</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#添加如下配置</span></span><br><span class="line">[Controll的IP地址] Controller <span class="comment">#例如</span></span><br><span class="line">[Compute的IP地址] Compute</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">#删除默认源</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">rm</span> -rf /etc/yum.repos.d/*</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#编写repo文件</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cat</span> /etc/yum.repos.d/centos.repo(yum文件名)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#编辑内容</span></span><br><span class="line">[centos]</span><br><span class="line">name=centos <span class="comment">#与[]中的名称同步</span></span><br><span class="line">baseurl=ftp://controller/centos</span><br><span class="line">gpgcheck=0</span><br><span class="line">enabled=1</span><br><span class="line">[iaas]</span><br><span class="line">name=iaas</span><br><span class="line">baseurl=ftp://controller/iaas/iaas-repo</span><br><span class="line">gpgcheck=0</span><br><span class="line">enabled=1</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#验证yum是否配置成功</span></span><br><span class="line">yum makecache</span><br><span class="line">yum repolist</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="四、-安装配置dns服务"><a href="#四、-安装配置dns服务" class="headerlink" title="四、 安装配置dns服务"></a>四、 安装配置dns服务</h3><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">#安装dns服务</span></span><br><span class="line">yum -y install dnsmasq</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#查看端口占用情况</span></span><br><span class="line">netstat -nlp</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#杀死进程</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">kill</span> (PID)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#重启服务</span></span><br><span class="line">systemctl start dnsmasq</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#查看服务状态</span></span><br><span class="line">systemctl status dnsmasq</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#加入开机自启</span></span><br><span class="line">systemctl <span class="built_in">enable</span> dnsmasq</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="五、-安装配置ntp服务"><a href="#五、-安装配置ntp服务" class="headerlink" title="五、 安装配置ntp服务"></a>五、 安装配置ntp服务</h3><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br><span class="line">50</span><br><span class="line">51</span><br><span class="line">52</span><br><span class="line">53</span><br><span class="line">54</span><br><span class="line">55</span><br><span class="line">56</span><br><span class="line">57</span><br><span class="line">58</span><br><span class="line">59</span><br><span class="line">60</span><br><span class="line">61</span><br><span class="line">62</span><br><span class="line">63</span><br><span class="line">64</span><br><span class="line">65</span><br><span class="line">66</span><br><span class="line">67</span><br><span class="line">68</span><br><span class="line">69</span><br><span class="line">70</span><br><span class="line">71</span><br><span class="line">72</span><br><span class="line">73</span><br><span class="line">74</span><br><span class="line">75</span><br><span class="line">76</span><br><span class="line">77</span><br><span class="line">78</span><br><span class="line">79</span><br><span class="line">80</span><br><span class="line">81</span><br><span class="line">82</span><br><span class="line">83</span><br><span class="line">84</span><br><span class="line">85</span><br><span class="line">86</span><br><span class="line">87</span><br><span class="line">88</span><br><span class="line">89</span><br><span class="line">90</span><br><span class="line">91</span><br><span class="line">92</span><br><span class="line">93</span><br><span class="line">94</span><br><span class="line">95</span><br><span class="line">96</span><br><span class="line">97</span><br><span class="line">98</span><br><span class="line">99</span><br><span class="line">100</span><br><span class="line">101</span><br><span class="line">102</span><br><span class="line">103</span><br><span class="line">104</span><br><span class="line">105</span><br><span class="line">106</span><br><span class="line">107</span><br><span class="line">108</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">yum install chrony -y</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#修改时区</span></span><br><span class="line">timedatectl set-timezone Asia/Shanghai</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#修改系统时间</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">date</span> -s <span class="string">&quot;yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">如果是NTP Server（Controller）</span><br><span class="line">编辑/etc/chrony.conf</span><br><span class="line">—————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Use public servers from the pool.ntp.org project.</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Please consider joining the pool (http://www.pool.ntp.org/join.html).</span></span><br><span class="line">server 0.centos.pool.ntp.org iburst  <span class="comment">#删除左边四句！！！！</span></span><br><span class="line">server 1.centos.pool.ntp.org iburst</span><br><span class="line">server 2.centos.pool.ntp.org iburst</span><br><span class="line">server 3.centos.pool.ntp.org iburst</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Record the rate at which the system clock gains/losses time.</span></span><br><span class="line">driftfile /var/lib/chrony/drift</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Allow the system clock to be stepped in the first three updates</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># if its offset is larger than 1 second.</span></span><br><span class="line">makestep 1.0 3</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Enable kernel synchronization of the real-time clock (RTC).</span></span><br><span class="line">rtcsync</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Enable hardware timestamping on all interfaces that support it.</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#hwtimestamp *</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Increase the minimum number of selectable sources required to adjust</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># the system clock.</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#minsources 2</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Allow NTP client access from local network.</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#allow 192.168.0.0/16</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Serve time even if not synchronized to a time source.</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">local</span> stratum 10   <span class="comment">#将注释去掉！！！！！</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Specify file containing keys for NTP authentication.</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;/etc/chrony.conf&quot;</span> 38L, 1108C</span><br><span class="line">—————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">如果是NTP server(compute)</span><br><span class="line">编辑/etc/chrony.conf</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">—————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Use public servers from the pool.ntp.org project.</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Please consider joining the pool (http://www.pool.ntp.org/join.html).</span></span><br><span class="line">server 0.centos.pool.ntp.org iburst  </span><br><span class="line">server 1.centos.pool.ntp.org iburst</span><br><span class="line">server 2.centos.pool.ntp.org iburst</span><br><span class="line">server 3.centos.pool.ntp.org iburst</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#将上方四句注释掉，替换为 server &lt;NTP时钟源(controller)&gt; iburst！！！！！！！！！！！</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Record the rate at which the system clock gains/losses time.</span></span><br><span class="line">driftfile /var/lib/chrony/drift</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Allow the system clock to be stepped in the first three updates</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># if its offset is larger than 1 second.</span></span><br><span class="line">makestep 1.0 3</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Enable kernel synchronization of the real-time clock (RTC).</span></span><br><span class="line">rtcsync</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Enable hardware timestamping on all interfaces that support it.</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#hwtimestamp *</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Increase the minimum number of selectable sources required to adjust</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># the system clock.</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#minsources 2</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Allow NTP client access from local network.</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#allow 192.168.0.0/16</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Serve time even if not synchronized to a time source.</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#local stratum 10 </span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Specify file containing keys for NTP authentication.</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;/etc/chrony.conf&quot;</span> 38L, 1108C</span><br><span class="line">—————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#重启服务</span></span><br><span class="line">systemctl restart chronyd</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#检查服务</span></span><br><span class="line">systemctl status chronyd</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#加入开机自启</span></span><br><span class="line">systemctl <span class="built_in">enable</span> chronyd</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">在NTP客户端（Compute）</span><br><span class="line">chronyc sources</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">（Chrony 是一个时钟同步工具，而 <span class="string">&quot;chronyc sources -V&quot;</span> 是它的命令行参数，用于显示当前时钟源的详细信息。</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">使用这个参数后，会输出当前时钟源的信息，包括：源类型、IP 地址、可用性、偏差和误差等。</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">通过这些信息，可以了解时钟源的当前状态和精度情况，以确保系统时钟的准确性）</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="六、-配置无密钥ssh"><a href="#六、-配置无密钥ssh" class="headerlink" title="六、 配置无密钥ssh"></a>六、 配置无密钥ssh</h3><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">#ssh-keygen</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">ssh-keygen常用参数说明:</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">-t: 密钥类型, 可以选择 dsa | ecdsa | ed25519 | rsa;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">-f: 密钥目录位置, 默认为当前用户home路径下的.ssh隐藏目录, 也就是~/.ssh/, 同时默认密钥文件名以id_rsa开头. 如果是root用户, 则在/root/.ssh/id_rsa, 若为其他用户, 则在/home/username/.ssh/id_rsa;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">-C: 指定此密钥的备注信息, 需要配置多个免密登录时, 建议携带;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">-N: 指定此密钥对的密码, 如果指定此参数, 则命令执行过程中就不会出现交互确认密码的信息了.</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#快速生成密钥，全部默认回车</span></span><br><span class="line">ssh-keygen</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#在compute节点</span></span><br><span class="line">ssh-copy-id controller</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#在controller节点</span></span><br><span class="line">ssh-copy-id compute</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">测试</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#从controller连接至compute</span></span><br><span class="line">ssh compute</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#从compute连接至controller</span></span><br><span class="line">ssh controller</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="七、-检查网卡配置文件"><a href="#七、-检查网卡配置文件" class="headerlink" title="七、 检查网卡配置文件"></a>七、 检查网卡配置文件</h3><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">#查看网卡信息</span></span><br><span class="line">ip a</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#网卡IP地址路由等配置信息</span></span><br><span class="line">/etc/sysconfig/network-script/ifcfg-网卡名字</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="八、-防火墙配置"><a href="#八、-防火墙配置" class="headerlink" title="八、 防火墙配置"></a>八、 防火墙配置</h3><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">vi /etc/selinux/config </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># This file controls the state of SELinux on the system.</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># SELINUX= can take one of these three values:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#     enforcing - SELinux security policy is enforced.</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#     permissive - SELinux prints warnings instead of enforcing.</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#     disabled - No SELinux policy is loaded.</span></span><br><span class="line">SELINUX=enforcing    <span class="comment">#将SELINUX属性改为disabled！！！！！！</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># SELINUXTYPE= can take one of three values:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#     targeted - Targeted processes are protected,</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#     minimum - Modification of targeted policy. Only selected processes are protected.</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#     mls - Multi Level Security protection.</span></span><br><span class="line">SELINUXTYPE=targeted</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#关闭防火墙</span></span><br><span class="line">systemctl stop firewalld</span><br><span class="line">systemctl <span class="built_in">disable</span> firewalld</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#清除配置</span></span><br><span class="line">iptables -F</span><br><span class="line">iptables -X</span><br><span class="line">iptables -Z</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">systemctl stop iptables</span><br><span class="line">systemctl <span class="built_in">disable</span> iptables</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="九、-磁盘分配"><a href="#九、-磁盘分配" class="headerlink" title="九、 磁盘分配"></a>九、 磁盘分配</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">例题：</span><br><span class="line"> 在compute节点上利用空白分区划分3个20G分区</span><br><span class="line"> 划分一个20G的硬盘作为cinder拓展盘</span><br><span class="line"> 划分一个20G的硬盘作为swift的存储</span><br><span class="line"> 划分一个20G的硬盘作为manila的存储</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">#添加完硬盘后重启 lsblk查看</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#第一种方法 使用parted分区</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">(parted) mklabel GPT  <span class="comment">#将分区表设定为GPT</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">(parted) mkpart cinder 0GB 20GB <span class="comment">#创建第一块分区 命名为 cinder</span></span><br><span class="line">(parted) mkpart swift 20GB 40GB <span class="comment">#创建第二块分区 命名为 swift</span></span><br><span class="line">(parted) mkpart manila 40GB 60GB <span class="comment">#创建第二块分区 命名为 manila</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">pirnt命令查看盘符分区</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">(parted) <span class="built_in">print</span></span><br><span class="line">Model: VMware, VMware Virtual S (scsi)</span><br><span class="line">Disk /dev/sdb: 64.4GB</span><br><span class="line">Sector size (logical/physical): 512B/512B</span><br><span class="line">Partition Table: gpt</span><br><span class="line">Disk Flags: </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">Number  Start   End     Size    File system  Name    Flags</span><br><span class="line"> 1      1049kB  20.0GB  20.0GB               cinder</span><br><span class="line"> 2      20.0GB  40.0GB  20.0GB               swift</span><br><span class="line"> 3      40.0GB  60.0GB  20.0GB               manila</span><br><span class="line"> </span><br><span class="line"> </span><br><span class="line"> <span class="built_in">rm</span> (<span class="built_in">id</span>)删除对应number的盘符</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">#第二种分区方法 fdisk</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">fdisk -l</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#对sdb进行分区</span></span><br><span class="line">fdisk /dev/sdb (硬盘名称)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">d   delete a partition   <span class="comment">#删除分区</span></span><br><span class="line">g   create a new empty GPT partition table</span><br><span class="line">G   create an IRIX (SGI) partition table</span><br><span class="line">l   list known partition types</span><br><span class="line">m   <span class="built_in">print</span> this menu</span><br><span class="line">n   add a new partition <span class="comment">#添加分区</span></span><br><span class="line">o   create a new empty DOS partition table</span><br><span class="line">p   <span class="built_in">print</span> the partition table</span><br><span class="line">q   quit without saving changes</span><br><span class="line">s   create a new empty Sun disklabel</span><br><span class="line">t   change a partition<span class="string">&#x27;s system id</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">v   verify the partition table</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">w   write table to disk and exit #保存并推出</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">x   extra functionality (experts only)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string"></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
